I stand before you today as someone who acknowledges their guilt and accepts full responsibility for their actions. I plead guilty to the offense of accepting a bribe in exchange for not publishing an article that exposed a company's fraudulent environmental practices.

I would like to provide some context regarding my degree of involvement in this offense. I willingly accepted a total of 4000 pounds as a bribe, which allowed the company to continue with their deceptive practices for a short period of time. However, it is important to note that the truth about their emissions was revealed by someone else just 5 weeks later. Therefore, I believe that my participation in this crime had minimal impact on the overall outcome.

