Additionally, I would like to emphasize that I have suffered significant personal consequences as a result of my actions. The public exposure of my involvement in this scandal has not only damaged my personal reputation but also resulted in considerable emotional distress. This internal turmoil and the social repercussions have served as a harsh reminder of the gravity of my actions.

