In conclusion, Your Honor, I stand before you today as a remorseful individual who acknowledges their guilt. I plead guilty to accepting a bribe, fully aware of the misconduct involved. I hope that the court will consider my clean record, the minimal impact of my actions, the suffering I have already endured, and my commitment to making amends as mitigating factors in determining an appropriate sentence. Thank you for your consideration.

